reviewText: The reality of life in an super populated island the jobs are few and the pay is bad not even minimum wage force the people to become a criminal or illegal way to make ends meet
this was a great movie i was very satisfied thank you! i chose to rate 5 stars because of the service and fro the greatness of the movie.

An engaging and rich depiction of a corrupt society and the difficult choices made by the protagonists, this film flows in a very naturalistic style. The acting is wonderful, more so when you consider that many of the cast are non-professionals! The script captures in a very real way the idiosyncrasies and attitudes of the modern Puerto Rican. In all, I truly recommend it.

Interesante y recomendable pelicula puertorriquea que refleja una sociedad que vive rodeada de delincuencia y corrupcin. Ambientada en la pequea isla caribea pero las tramas que aparecen en la pelicula podran haber sido adaptadas a cualquier lugar del mundo actual donde delincuencia y corrupcin van de la mano sin que nadie haga algo por evitarlo.
